<ab facs="#facs_364_r1l5">auf <expan>morg<ex>en</ex></expan> ſunntag bey vns geſucht ſolt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> etc . das haben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_364_r1l6">wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd haben <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> ~ dıe <expan>teıchſl<ex>er</ex></expan> . der wır mechtıg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_364_r1l7">ſeyn für vns beſandt vnd mıt Jn <expan>ernſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt / dıe <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_364_r1l8">vns <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> / daʒ ſıe der ſache nıht <expan>m<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒuſchıken haben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_364_r1l9">vnd Jren <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> den <expan>geıſtlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> angee . als ewch das nehſt bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_364_r1l11">vns auch wol geſagt ward / Vnd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_364_r1l10">wıe </ab></add> wol wır <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Jrs <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> nıht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_364_r1l12">mechtıg ſeyn vnd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_364_line_1595394653068_23">er </ab></add> der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> nıht ıſt doch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Eyſtett </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_364_r1l14"> ʒu eren vnd eẅch ʒu lıeb / haben wır 
<del rend="strikethrough">Jn </del> fleıſſıg 
<del rend="strikethrough">gebetten </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_364_r1l13">mıt Jm geredt </ab></add> vmb </ab>
